$NetBSD: patch-ak,v 1.2 2015/01/29 11:34:41 thomasklausner Exp $

Handle NetBSD/powerpc the same as FreeBSD and OpenBSD.

Sent to libffi upstream as:
https://github.com/atgreen/libffi/pull/176

--- js/src/ctypes/libffi/configure.orig	2014-09-28 08:30:06.000000000 +0000
+++ js/src/ctypes/libffi/configure
@@ -17226,7 +17226,7 @@ case "$host" in
   powerpc-*-aix* | rs6000-*-aix*)
 	TARGET=POWERPC_AIX; TARGETDIR=powerpc
 	;;
-  powerpc-*-freebsd* | powerpc-*-openbsd*)
+  powerpc-*-freebsd* | powerpc-*-openbsd* | powerpc-*-netbsd*)
 	TARGET=POWERPC_FREEBSD; TARGETDIR=powerpc
 	HAVE_LONG_DOUBLE_VARIANT=1
 	;;
